    "description": "Sharekhan Global Group invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Credit Analyst at our Varanasi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Sharekhan Global Group:\nSharekhan Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sharekhan Global Group!",
